(Emergency board meeting tomorrow.)

244
00:17:21.610 --> 00:17:22.870
(Dismissal of Director Kim Min Kyu.)

245
00:17:30.721 --> 00:17:32.350
I'm back.

246
00:17:35.350 --> 00:17:36.421
Doctor.

247
00:17:37.290 --> 00:17:38.320
Hoktal.

248
00:17:41.530 --> 00:17:42.560
Brother?

249
00:17:44.261 --> 00:17:47.130
I'm not scared. I'm not scared at all.

250
00:17:47.600 --> 00:17:48.701
Doctor.

251
00:17:51.300 --> 00:17:53.971
Where did everyone go without me?

252
00:17:55.171 --> 00:17:58.481
They're all so mean. How could they?

253
00:17:58.481 --> 00:18:01.810
It's my birthday. If I were in the US, there'd be a party.

254
00:18:02.310 --> 00:18:04.120
No one cares.

255
00:18:05.251 --> 00:18:08.020
- Hello. - What the... What's going on?

256
00:18:08.151 --> 00:18:09.651
Happy birthday.

257
00:18:11.860 --> 00:18:15.491
Happy birthday to you

258
00:18:15.491 --> 00:18:18.530
Happy birthday to you

259
00:18:18.530 --> 00:18:21.870
Happy birthday dear Ssanip

260
00:18:21.870 --> 00:18:24.671
Happy birthday to you

261
00:18:32.540 --> 00:18:35.880
You're all so childish.

262
00:18:36.110 --> 00:18:38.120
A surprise party?

263
00:18:38.120 --> 00:18:41.020
We don't do this on the east coast.

264
00:18:41.421 --> 00:18:44.391
Things like this don't impress me.

265
00:18:45.461 --> 00:18:46.590
I'm impressed.

266
00:18:47.360 --> 00:18:49.330
Thank you.

267
00:18:50.161 --> 00:18:51.860
Did you think we didn't know?

268
00:18:51.860 --> 00:18:54.001
- Blow out the candles. - Blow the candles.

269
00:18:54.100 --> 00:18:55.600
Blow the candles.

270
00:18:55.600 --> 00:18:57.001
Let's all live together.

271
00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:13.951
Brother, this is incredible. Did you make it?

272
00:19:14.320 --> 00:19:18.120
I knew it. I just put together a little feast.

273
00:19:18.120 --> 00:19:19.590
The cake's amazing.

274
00:19:20.991 --> 00:19:22.461
I chose it.

275
00:19:22.931 --> 00:19:24.330
With my help.

276
00:19:28.501 --> 00:19:30.641
I feel like overturning the table.

277
00:19:30.741 --> 00:19:31.770
Here's yours.

278
00:19:38.681 --> 00:19:39.711
Your present.

279
00:19:41.511 --> 00:19:43.350
What could be inside?

280
00:19:45.020 --> 00:19:46.050
What is it?

281
00:19:47.451 --> 00:19:48.790
(Citron bread)

282
00:19:48.790 --> 00:19:49.850
Citron bread?

283
00:19:51.721 --> 00:19:53.731
Brother, what does this mean?

284
00:19:53.731 --> 00:19:56.431
We heard you cry whenever you see this.

285
00:19:56.630 --> 00:19:58.060
I wanted to see you eat it and cry.

286
00:19:58.100 --> 00:19:59.800
Why you...

287
00:20:01.971 --> 00:20:04.401
- You're crying already. - What are you saying?

288
00:20:04.401 --> 00:20:05.701
I see tears.

289
00:20:05.701 --> 00:20:07.511
He's crying, he's crying.

290
00:20:10.741 --> 00:20:13.981
Shall I make him cry even more?

291
00:20:14.481 --> 00:20:15.550
With this gift.

292
00:20:15.681 --> 00:20:19.020
Is that a new one? How many terabytes?

293
00:20:19.251 --> 00:20:21.451
The present is the video on this.

294
00:20:22.020 --> 00:20:23.820
It's a gift from Aji 3 who just finished...

295
00:20:24.620 --> 00:20:25.820
her first outing.

296
00:20:44.481 --> 00:20:46.580
She must be really cold.

297
00:20:47.780 --> 00:20:50.280
What's she wearing? It's so thin.

298
00:20:51.320 --> 00:20:53.221
Don't wander around, and go straight home.

299
00:20:54.391 --> 00:20:55.951
Or you will end up like me.

300
00:20:56.820 --> 00:20:59.520
What does it mean to end up like you?

301
00:21:02.030 --> 00:21:04.100
I have no one to see.

302
00:21:06.231 --> 00:21:08.201
There is no one waiting for me.

303
00:21:10.231 --> 00:21:12.471
No one is interested in me.

304
00:21:17.181 --> 00:21:20.080
You know how to take the bus, right? Get going.

305
00:21:30.290 --> 00:21:31.491
You did a good job.

306
00:21:44.070 --> 00:21:45.770
Thank you.

307
00:21:50.911 --> 00:21:51.981
You're pretty.

308
00:21:53.911 --> 00:21:54.951
Aji 3.

309
00:21:57.050 --> 00:21:59.251
Aji 3, where are you going?

310
00:22:03.120 --> 00:22:04.820
Aji 3, are you okay?

311
00:22:05.891 --> 00:22:06.991
Let's go home.

312
00:22:25.941 --> 00:22:29.181
We wanted Aji 3 to commune with people.

313
00:22:30.481 --> 00:22:31.550
As you saw,

314
00:22:32.380 --> 00:22:35.820
she did much better than we had hoped.

315
00:22:36.891 --> 00:22:37.961
Not just us.

316
00:22:38.721 --> 00:22:42.761
Min Kyu and Ji A, you both did well too.

317
00:22:44.030 --> 00:22:46.401
Why do we make robots?

318
00:22:47.201 --> 00:22:48.931
I think that Aji 3's memories...

319
00:22:50.540 --> 00:22:51.570
will answer that.

320
00:22:52.401 --> 00:22:53.540
It's heartbreaking,

321
00:22:54.711 --> 00:22:56.711
but as promised, I think it's time...

322
00:22:57.540 --> 00:22:58.880
to change Aji 3's face.

323
00:22:59.310 --> 00:23:03.481
We'll leave just the patterns of the emotions she procured,

324
00:23:04.020 --> 00:23:07.550
and delete every video including the private ones...

325
00:23:08.350 --> 00:23:10.691
she took of Min Kyu and Ji A.

326
00:23:12.961 --> 00:23:13.961
Then...

327
00:23:14.590 --> 00:23:16.290
we'll begin on...

328
00:23:17.530 --> 00:23:18.560
our new android robot.

329
00:23:19.901 --> 00:23:21.130
I'm sure that Aji 3...

330
00:23:23.070 --> 00:23:24.270
would want that too.

331
00:23:25.100 --> 00:23:28.641
She'd want us to make her memories more beautiful.

332
00:23:29.911 --> 00:23:30.911
So...

333
00:23:31.840 --> 00:23:33.141
let's all...

334
00:23:35.951 --> 00:23:37.020
say our goodbyes.

335
00:23:41.120 --> 00:23:43.891
You helped us come this far.

336
00:23:45.191 --> 00:23:46.590
The patterns you left...

337
00:23:47.231 --> 00:23:48.860
will continue in the next robot.

338
00:23:49.391 --> 00:23:50.401
That's how...

339
00:23:51.231 --> 00:23:52.761
we'll remember you forever.

340
00:23:54.701 --> 00:23:56.870
Bye, Aji 3.

341
00:23:58.100 --> 00:24:00.141
I'm really sorry for sending you...

342
00:24:01.310 --> 00:24:02.641
to Martin.

343
00:24:04.080 --> 00:24:05.911
I really wanted to say that.

344
00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:10.880
I'll tell the next robot about you.

345
00:24:12.380 --> 00:24:13.421
You...

346
00:24:14.951 --> 00:24:16.350
will not disappear.

347
00:24:17.820 --> 00:24:20.491
I know you liked me more than anyone.

348
00:24:21.530 --> 00:24:22.931
I will remember you,

349
00:24:24.401 --> 00:24:25.461
Aji 3.

350
00:24:27.530 --> 00:24:30.130
- Goodbye, Aji 3. - Goodbye, Aji 3.

351
00:24:38.511 --> 00:24:40.481
Aji 3's last video...

352
00:24:40.580 --> 00:24:44.020
captured Martin confessing to killing Chairman Park.

353
00:24:44.550 --> 00:24:48.691
I think he let his guard down because she was a robot.

354
00:24:50.491 --> 00:24:52.590
Interpol will love this.

355
00:24:53.120 --> 00:24:55.630
They will protect Jang Doo Sam for sure now.

356
00:24:57.630 --> 00:24:58.661
That's good.

357
00:24:59.731 --> 00:25:02.231
We have reporters on standby.

358
00:25:02.630 --> 00:25:03.941
We can go right ahead.

359
00:25:04.241 --> 00:25:05.701
When the board meeting ends,

360
00:25:06.141 --> 00:25:10.280
someone is bound to tell them what just happened.

361
00:25:11.441 --> 00:25:13.651
We can't get blood on our hands.

362
00:25:24.761 --> 00:25:25.921
(Emergency Board Meeting)

363
00:25:25.921 --> 00:25:28.731
We shall begin the emergency board meeting.

364
00:25:29.060 --> 00:25:31.701
The agenda is the dismissal of Director Kim Min Kyu.

365
00:25:32.060 --> 00:25:35.731
The cause is as you were all informed. An illness.

366
00:25:57.661 --> 00:25:58.661
He's here.

367
00:26:08.300 --> 00:26:10.171
(KM Financial Director Kim Min Kyu Press Conference)

368
00:26:16.810 --> 00:26:18.681
(KM Financial Director Kim Min Kyu Press Conference)

369
00:26:22.850 --> 00:26:24.721
I'm KM Financial's director...

370
00:26:26.151 --> 00:26:27.151
Kim Min Kyu.

371
00:26:29.251 --> 00:26:30.421
I also...

372
00:26:38.530 --> 00:26:39.731
suffer from...

373
00:26:43.201 --> 00:26:44.270
a human allergy.

374
00:27:21.070 --> 00:27:22.070
(I'm Not a Robot)

375
00:27:22.070 --> 00:27:23.780
His allergy isn't completely cured yet?

376
00:27:23.780 --> 00:27:26.011
Is he allowed to go outside without you?

377
00:27:26.011 --> 00:27:28.681
It's not over yet. We still have a chance.

378
00:27:28.681 --> 00:27:31.520
Why is he always so harsh on me?

379
00:27:31.550 --> 00:27:35.221
We used to be friends. How could he treat me this way?

380
00:27:35.820 --> 00:27:38.661
Don't you need me there to fight?

381
00:27:38.661 --> 00:27:40.060
No, it's okay.

382
00:27:40.330 --> 00:27:43.830
Wherever I may be, I know that you'll always be by my side.

383
00:27:44.100 --> 00:27:47.330
I think it's going to be okay this time.

